{"article_id":"TXJpXJP313P8COUl","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The former Trump adviser","depth":8},{"id":1,"text":"whose remarks in a London pub sparked the US inquiry into possible collusion with Russia","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"has been sentenced to 14 days in jail .","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"George Papadopoulos , 31 , told the court in Washington DC","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"he was a `` patriotic American ''","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"who made a mistake","depth":10},{"id":6,"text":"by lying .","depth":10},{"id":7,"text":"He pleaded guilty last October to lying to the FBI about the timing of meetings with alleged go-betweens for Moscow .","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"He was the first former Trump aide","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"arrested in the probe into an alleged Kremlin plot","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"to sway the 2016 US vote .","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"US President Donald Trump reacted","depth":5},{"id":12,"text":"by taking an apparent swipe at the cost of the investigation into the former aide .","depth":5},{"id":13,"text":"In Friday 's sentencing , Papadopoulos was also handed 12 months of supervised release , 200 hours of community service , and a fine of $ 9,500","depth":5},{"id":14,"text":"( £7,350 ) .","depth":5},{"id":15,"text":"He said in court","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"that his `` entire life has been turned upside down ''","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"and he hoped `` for a second chance","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"to redeem myself '' .","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"Papadopoulos concluded","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"by saying","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"`` this investigation has global implications ,","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"and the truth matters '' .","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"The Chicago native was a London-based petroleum analyst","depth":6},{"id":24,"text":"before he joined the Trump campaign in March 2016 as a volunteer foreign policy adviser .","depth":6},{"id":25,"text":"Papadopoulos soon made contact with a mysterious Maltese academic , Joseph Mifsud .","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"The professor told Papadopoulos","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"the Russians had `` dirt '' on Mr Trump 's Democratic presidential rival Hillary Clinton in the form of `` thousands of emails '' .","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"In the following months , thousands of emails","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"linked to the Clinton campaign","depth":11},{"id":30,"text":"were published by Wikileaks .","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"The young political operative told Mr Trump , then a Republican presidential candidate , and other members of the campaign 's national security team","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"that he could set up a meeting with President Vladimir Putin ahead of the 2016 election .","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"A pre-sentencing statement last week read :","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"`` While some in the room rebuffed George 's offer ,","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"Mr Trump nodded with approval","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"and deferred to Mr Sessions ,","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"who appeared to like the idea","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"and stated","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"that the campaign should look into it . ''","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"Papadopoulos told CNN in an interview","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"aired on Friday","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"that Mr Trump `` gave me a sort of a nod ''","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"and `` was n't committed either way '' about the idea of a meeting with the Russian leader .","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"But he said","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"then-senator and now-Attorney General Jeff Sessions `` was actually enthusiastic '' .","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"Last November , Mr Sessions testified to Congress","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"that he had `` pushed back '' against Papadopoulos ' offer .","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"American authorities were alerted in mid-2016","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"after Papadopoulos told an Australian diplomat during a drinking session in a London pub about his meetings with Professor Mifsud .","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"The envoy told US investigators ,","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"shortly after the emails","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"hacked from the Democratic Party","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"were leaked .","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"When the FBI interviewed Papadopoulos in January 2017 ,","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"he falsely claimed","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"he had met two individuals with Russian ties","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"before he joined the president 's team in March 2016 .","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"He had actually met them","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"after joining Mr Trump 's campaign .","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"One individual was a Russian woman","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"whom Papadopoulos believed","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"had connections to the Russian government .","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"In July 2018 , the US Department of Justice charged 12 Russian intelligence officers with hacking Democratic officials .","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"Prosecutors said","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"Papadopoulos 's lack of cooperation with investigators meant they were unable to effectively question or detain Mr Mifsud .","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"The professor has since left the United States .","depth":8},{"id":67,"text":"No connection between Mr Misfud and the hacked emails has been proven .","depth":5},{"id":68,"text":"The Democratic National Committee ,","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"which is suing Russia , the Trump campaign and WikiLeaks over the alleged election interference in the 2016 ,","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"filed a court document on Friday ,","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"saying","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"Mr Mifsud `` was missing","depth":11},{"id":73,"text":"and may be deceased '' ,","depth":11},{"id":74,"text":"without any further explanation ,","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"according to Bloomberg News .","depth":7},{"id":76,"text":"It referred to him as a key figure","depth":7},{"id":77,"text":"to have evaded the Mueller inquiry .","depth":7},{"id":78,"text":"`` I made a dreadful mistake ,","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"but I am a good man","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"who is eager for redemption , ''","depth":10},{"id":81,"text":"Papadopoulos said .","depth":8},{"id":82,"text":"He said","depth":8},{"id":83,"text":"he lied","depth":9},{"id":84,"text":"not to impede investigation","depth":10},{"id":85,"text":"but `` to preserve a perhaps misguided loyalty to his master '' .","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"Judge Randolph Moss said","depth":8},{"id":87,"text":"he took the `` genuine remorse '' into consideration for the sentencing .","depth":8},{"id":88,"text":"The only other person","depth":11},{"id":89,"text":"to be sentenced in the investigation","depth":11},{"id":90,"text":"- lawyer Alex Van Der Zwaan -","depth":10},{"id":91,"text":"received 30 days in prison .","depth":9},{"id":92,"text":"His judge referred to his regret as `` muted '' .","depth":8},{"id":93,"text":"Outside court on Friday , Papadopoulos ' lawyer , Thomas Breen , said","depth":3},{"id":94,"text":"his client was a `` fool ''","depth":4},{"id":95,"text":"and had acted `` stupidly ''","depth":5},{"id":96,"text":"in lying to the FBI .","depth":5},{"id":97,"text":"But the attorney said","depth":4},{"id":98,"text":"`` the president of the United States hindered this investigation more","depth":5},{"id":99,"text":"than Papadopoulos ever could '' .","depth":5},{"id":100,"text":"He said","depth":4},{"id":101,"text":"Mr Trump had hampered the inquiry","depth":5},{"id":102,"text":"by calling it a `` witch hunt '' and `` fake news '' .","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":205,"left":195,"right":204,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":195,"left":125,"right":194,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":125,"left":115,"right":124,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":115,"left":113,"right":114,"relation